summaries.short: After sending three men into orbit around the moon, landing them on the surface was the next goal.
summaries.full: After sending three men into orbit around the moon, landing them on the surface was the next goal. In order to achieve that, the Apollo project had to design a second spacecraft: the Lunar Module, which took 7 years of designing building and testing.

summaries.short: 1968 was looking very bleak. But then, NASA took a bold step sending the Apollo 8 on the first journey towards the moon.
summaries.full: With all that happened that year, the Vietnam War, the death of Kennedy and Luther King, strikes and protest all over the globe; 1968 was looking very bleak. But then, NASA took a bold step sending the Apollo 8 on the first journey towards the moon.
